Package com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Controllers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateMoodController
    CreateMoodController handles the creation of some mood event that a participant would like to make.
    DeleteMoodController
    DeleteMoodController will delete mood events from the participant's mood event list.
    EditMoodController
    EditMoodController is similar to CreateMoodController in that it will editMoodEvent the mood event list of the participant with a new mood event.
    ElasticController
    Elastic search controller superclass that is used to createMoodEvent the variety of controllers used throughout the program.
    ElasticMoodController
    ElasticMoodController handles any changes regarding moods, whether it would be updating, deleting, or adding moods.
    ElasticMoodController.AddMoodEventTask
    AddMoodEventTask adds a mood event into the elastic server.
    ElasticMoodController.AddOfflineMoodEventTask
    Add Task that utilizes an arraylist of mood events that handles the offline mood events that needs to be added into the server upon online reconnection.
    ElasticMoodController.DeleteMoodEventTask
    DeleteMoodEventTask is used when the participant would like to delete their mood events.
    ElasticMoodController.DeleteOfflineMoodEventTask
    DeleteTask that handles an arraylist of mood events to properly bulk delete.
    ElasticMoodController.UpdateMoodTask
    Update task to editMoodEvent the mood events as you try to edit your mood.
    ElasticMoodController.UpdateOfflineMoodTask
    Update task that utilizes the arraylist of mood events that needs to be editted upon reconnection of the network
    ElasticParticipantController
    ElasticParticipantController handles all elastic requests in regards to participants.
    ElasticParticipantController.AddParticipantTask
    AddParticipantTask deals with adding new participants into the server when the participant signs up at the login page.
    ElasticParticipantController.FindAllParticipantsTask
    Similar to the FindParticipantTask, this method will search for all participants that have registered themselves into the server.
    ElasticParticipantController.FindParticipantTask
    FindParticipantTask is used to find a participant with a certain login name (case insensitive).
    ElasticParticipantController.UpdateParticipantTask
    Elastic task method used to editMoodEvent a participant.
    FileManager

    ParticipantController
    Created by adong on 3/20/17.
